getWhereCondition

protected java.lang.String getWhereCondition()
Returns the where condition for the select statement to process the inquiry. See the code of subclasses of Search for samples how this may be implemented. In the simplest case it looks like return DbFieldName like '%" + UIfield.getText() + "%'";
